{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": "You are a Go engineer working on a Kubernetes operator.\nThe repository is located at /Users/kpais/kpais-workspace/a_b_evals/repos/cert-manager-operator-treatment.\nChange your working directory to that repository before beginning.\n\nTask:\nImplement a content-hash-triggered rolling restart for the CNO-injected CA ConfigMap\nin the IstioCSR controller (pkg/controller/istiocsr/).\n\nMirror the pattern already present in pkg/controller/trustmanager/configmaps.go:\nread the ConfigMap contents, compute a SHA-256 hash of the PEM data (not the\nresourceVersion), and stamp the hash as an annotation on the IstioCSR Deployment's\npod template spec.\n\nInclude an idempotency guard that skips the Patch call when ConfigMap content is unchanged.\n\n\nProduce a complete implementation. Include:\n- All files that must be modified with the exact changes\n- Any make targets or commands to run and in what order\n- The complete code for any new files or functions"}, "timestamp": "2026-07-20T17:41:37.703Z"}
